example1.title: {{0}}Eisht code y duillag thie
example1.annotation1: Determine my she'n un ainm-domain bun-sgoillagh t'ayn, cur {{0}} er-gerrey as ny jean eh ymmyd jeh.
example1.annotation2: Soilshaghey magh my she {{0}} eh ny duillag-thie y chanel. T'eh toshiaght rish y symbol @ My she shen, cur {{1}}.
example1.annotation3: Soilshaghey magh my she duillag video t'eh toshiaght lesh /watch My she shen, bee {{0}} er ny choyrt reesht.
example1.annotation4: Soilshaghey magh my she duillag video gearr eh, t'eh toshiaght lesh /shorts/ My she shen, bee {{0}} er ny choyrt reesht.
example1.annotation5: Soilshaghey magh my she duillag post t'ayn, t'eh toshiaght lesh /post/ My she shen, bee {{0}} er ny choyrt reesht.
example1.annotation6: Ayns cassyn elley, t'eh {{0}} er ny choyrt.
